timing_extract..._checks_as_arc(25.10)  timing_extract..._checks_as_arc(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_write_clock_checks_as_arc

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_write_clock_checks_as_arc

       {true | false}

       Default : false

       When  set  to  true, the clock checks (min_period and min_pulse_width )
       are modelled as arcs in the extracted timing models (ETM). Clock  check
       arcs  will  be  modelled as a single dimensional table with constrained
       and reference pin as clock pin itself.

       When set to false, clock checks are modelled as scalar numbers  in  the
       extracted ETM.

       To set this global variable, use set command.

